summary: This is an internal FBI email discussing scheduling for Epstein-related briefings, specifically coordinating dates for briefings in the Miami and New York field offices in September 2019.

events.title: Proposed Miami Field Office Briefing
events.description: A briefing related to the Epstein case is proposed to be held at the Miami Field Office on this date.

events.title: Proposed New York Field Office Briefing
events.description: A briefing related to the Epstein case is proposed to be held in New York on this date, after the Miami briefing.

keyFacts: Internal FBI communication regarding scheduling of Epstein briefings in September 2019.
The Miami Field Office space was not available on September 23 but was available on September 15.
The email proposes holding the Miami briefing first, followed by the New York briefing on September 23.
